<m_navbar bg="#f2f3ff" title="{{ title }}"/>
<view class="_page">
  <view class="sub-title">1. 基础主题</view>
  <view class="flex-box">
    <view class="flex-item-3-left">
      <m_button>确认</m_button>
    </view>
    <view class="flex-item-3-center">
      <m_button theme="success">成功</m_button>
    </view>
    <view class="flex-item-3-right">
      <m_button theme="error">取消</m_button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="sub-title">2. 轻快主题</view>
  <view class="flex-box">
    <view class="flex-item-3-left">
      <m_button theme="primary-light">确认</m_button>
    </view>
    <view class="flex-item-3-center">
      <m_button theme="success-light">成功</m_button>
    </view>
    <view class="flex-item-3-right">
      <m_button theme="error-light">取消</m_button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="sub-title">3. 功能按钮</view>
  <view class="flex-box">
    <view class="flex-item-3-left">
      <m_button icon="search">搜索</m_button>
    </view>
    <view class="flex-item-3-center">
      <m_button loading>加载中</m_button>
    </view>
    <view class="flex-item-3-right">
      <m_button disabled icon='app'>禁用</m_button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="sub-title">4. 自定义能力</view>
  <view class="disc">a. 圆角</view>
  <view class="flex-box">
    <view class="flex-item-3-left">
      <m_button theme="primary" shape="round">确认</m_button>
    </view>
    <view class="flex-item-3-center">
      <m_button shape="round" theme="success">成功</m_button>
    </view>
    <view class="flex-item-3-right">
      <m_button shape="round" theme="error">取消</m_button>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="disc">b. 尺寸</view>
  <view class="flex-box">
    <m_button theme="primary" size="large">确认</m_button>
  </view>
  <view class="flex-box">
    <m_button theme="success">成功</m_button>
  </view>
  <view class="flex-box">
    <m_button theme="error" size="small">取消</m_button>
  </view>
  <view class="disc">c. 自定义颜色</view>
  <view class="flex-box">
    <view class="flex-item-3-left">
      <m_button bg="skyblue" color="white" theme=''>天蓝色</m_button>
    </view>
    <view class="flex-item-3-center">
      <m_button bg="transparent" color="orangeed" theme=''>透明色</m_button>
    </view>
    <view class="flex-item-3-right">
      <m_button bg="purple" theme=''>紫色</m_button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="sub-title">5. 注意</view>
  <view class="disc">a. 内置主题颜色优先级高于自定义颜色，如想自定义颜色，请先清空默认主题。</view>
  <view class="disc">b. 图标显示是有条件的，当尺寸为small时不显示图标。当按钮状态为loading时，loading图标会覆盖原图标。</view>
  <view class="disc">c. 按钮中仅存在图标而不存在描述文字时，按钮尺寸是固定的，无法改变。</view>
</view>
<view class="blank"></view>
